[color=red][size=18]Spec Racer Ford Challenge Series @ [b] Mount Panorama Circuit (Bathurst)[/b]
Week 8 of 12 - 2018 Season 3 [/size][/color]
Race Distance: [b]10 laps[/b], approximately 25 minutes
World Record lap time: [b]2:34.394[/b] by Jairo Via
(n.b. random/dynamic weather impacts lap times greatly)

This week we travel to Australia to visit the famous Mount Panorama Circuit, also known simply as Bathurst. Mount Panorama can be intimidating and frustrating. If you're unfamiliar with the track take it easy and chances are you will enjoy it.
It is [b]particularly[/b] important to practice before racing on this track.

Target "planned" SoF race is usually 20:45 GMT Sunday, immediately following the Weekend Warriors league race.

